{{Quote|Can we all agree that song is the best thing that ever struck this planet?|R-3X|<ref name="Cantina" />}}
"'''Droid World'''" was a [[Huttese]]<ref name="karaoke">[[Leland Chee]]'s karaoke playlist {{C|[[:File:LelandChee-Karaoke-Playlist-LFL.jpg|screenshot]]}}</ref> [[Music|song]] performed by [[Sentient 7 and the Clankers]], featuring on their album "[[Listen Up Meatbags]]." The song was played by the [[droid]] [[DJ (occupation)|DJ]] [[R-3X]] at [[Oga's Cantina]] in the [[City|town]] of [[Black Spire Outpost]] on the [[planet]] [[Batuu]].<ref name="Cantina" /> R-3X considered "Droid World" to be a smashing hit<ref name="A Crash of Fate">''[[A Crash of Fate]]''</ref> and claimed that it was the best thing to ever strike the planet.<ref name="Cantina" />

